data.description: Only 7 years old, this is a quality built home that sits on 2.22 acres. The first floor is smooth concreate with in- floor radiant heat. An open floor plan creates a great space to entertain. The custom kitchen is solid alder cabinets, a farmhouse sink in the island, floating shelves, and maple butcher block counter tops....a cooks dream. There is a first floor primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings that offers a full bathroom. On the second floor is an additional living space to hang out in, 3 more bedrooms and a full bathroom. Outside is a private oasis with 2.2 acres on a partially wooded lot. There is a covered patio with a concrete slab to relax and enjoy nature. Patio doors lead into the home from the patio. An attached 2 stall garage completes this amazing home. Located close to Carthage and about 20 minutes to Fort Drum.
